Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.46,0:00:06.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Star" is a fascinating word.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:07.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can refer to both culprits and actors!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.84,0:00:09.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Time is running out, Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.49,0:00:10.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's solve this case...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.93,0:00:12.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And get her back before the show starts!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.84,0:00:14.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seeing through to the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.39,0:00:16.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I look like a child, but have the intellect of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:18.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.21,0:00:23.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, we felt the same light the moment we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.10,0:00:29.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, lots and lots of the same emotions filled our eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.85,0:00:35.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although the signals you sent destroyed my theory...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.75,0:00:41.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These feelings were always beyond your reach
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:47.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, let's fight, go against our morals...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.78,0:00:52.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And aim for a wider world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.30,0:00:59.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, glimmering star, shine over us forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.15,0:01:05.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This way, we won't lose the dreams we had when we were young...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.13,0:01:11.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't care if this town changes someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.10,0:01:17.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only thing I don't want to change is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.20,0:01:23.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, glimmering star, shine over us forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.90,0:01:29.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This way, we won't lose the dreams we had when we were young...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.00,0:01:39.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only thing I don't want to change is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.51,0:01:47.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Itou Tamanosuke's popular traveling\Ntheater troupe came to our town to perform a play.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.35,0:01:50.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This time, they'd be performing an\Nadaptation of "The Legend of the Bamboo Cutter."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.98,0:01:57.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, Kataoka Renge{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who was supposed to\Nplay Princess Kaguya, the main character, was kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:02:00.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once the police started investigating...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.24,0:02:04.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I discovered it was a staged\Nkidnapping that Renge{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had planned herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.04,0:02:10.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, Renge{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was not at the confinement area.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.50,0:02:15.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somehow, she was actually kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.05,0:02:18.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The case started to progress...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.01,0:02:21.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And now, the curtains begin to rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:28.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Simultaneous Stages of Advancing and Kidnapping:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.23,0:02:28.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Part 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.20,0:02:45.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once upon a time, there was an\Nold man who harvested bamboo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.70,0:02:47.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.12,0:02:48.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The play started!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:51.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Princess Kaguya isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:53.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:01.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leader could it be that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.47,0:03:02.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:04.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really intend to let her be in the actual play?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.85,0:03:07.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's the main character, she's Kaguya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:12.05,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Azuma Yoichi (28)\N{\fs8} Tamanosuke Theater Troupe Member
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:12.05,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Sawamura Kantarou (23)\N{\fs8} Tamanosuke Theater Troupe Member
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.88,0:03:11.00,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Her lines aren't easy either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:12.08,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.27,0:03:13.41,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,No worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.62,0:03:14.77,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I've changed the script.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.93,0:03:17.19,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Everyone, please memorize this quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.14,0:03:19.88,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Onoe Mataroku (35)\N{\fs8} Tamanosuke Theater Troupe Member
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:26.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I added more scenes from Kaguya's childhood\Nand removed the scenes that show her later years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:31.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later on, I'll redirect Kaguya's stage direction as\Nwell as the lighting so that her face is mostly hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:38.32,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,However, she has to show her face during\Nthe climax scene where she goes to the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:35.73,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,0)}Itou Tamanosuke (17)\N{\fs9} Tamanosuke Theater Troupe Leader
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:40.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, this isn't going to work...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.38,0:03:42.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Traveling and performing this is our life."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:45.11,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,0)}Ichimura Kikuno (40)\N{\fs8} Tamanosuke Theater Troupe Member
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.12,0:03:45.07,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"When it rains, it pours."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.88,0:03:52.61,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,0)}Bandouhiko Emon (50)\N{\fs9} Tamanosuke Theater Troupe Member
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.21,0:03:50.34,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"If we combine our efforts in times like these,\Nwe can create an outstanding performance."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:52.63,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,That was a famous line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:55.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the old man -l mean, the predecessor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.27,0:04:00.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's trust Renge{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} to come back\Nand just do the best we can for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:01.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, but-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please let me do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.99,0:04:04.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.16,0:04:06.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The audience is out there waiting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.95,0:04:08.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cancelling it on them would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:11.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please let me do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.45,0:04:12.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.67,0:04:14.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:17.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.88,0:04:19.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since she asked so sincerely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:21.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We have to, since she asked us so sincerely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:22.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.38,0:04:24.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be under your guidance then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:28.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.18,0:04:29.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:31.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tamanosuke{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.47,0:04:34.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When is the climax in the performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:35.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.31,0:04:40.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The whole play is two hours, so\Nit'd be about an hour and a half in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:41.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although that's just an estimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.48,0:04:46.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that means we just have to\Nfind Renge{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-oneesan{\r} by then, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.61,0:04:49.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have a clue or something\Nthat could help us find her, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.49,0:04:50.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:51.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:52.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've been waiting for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:55.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:57.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a call for the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.92,0:04:58.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.25,0:05:00.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:02.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never asked for help from you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:04.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I'm coming, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.76,0:05:07.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tamanosuke{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:11.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My part isn't until the second half, which is in an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:14.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until then, I'll help look for Renge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:15.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.44,0:05:18.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The case was progressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.35,0:05:25.35,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Oonuki Souichi (38)\N{\fs11} Kataoka's Private Secretary
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.44,0:05:25.50,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me, officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:31.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We are approaching the parking lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.97,0:05:49.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? He seems to have received\Nan envelope with something in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.97,0:05:55.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It says to drive in the designated car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:56.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,License plate number...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.23,0:05:57.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,License plate number...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:01.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:27.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer, there is a cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:28.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:31.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:32.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:34.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:36.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:40.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was told to drive north of Takayama Road.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.98,0:06:42.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will follow their directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.79,0:07:00.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The girl was incomparably beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:05.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her presence lit up the dark room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.55,0:07:13.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're almost up, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:17.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.31,0:07:18.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I need to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.69,0:07:25.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't this the place where Renge{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was kept?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.82,0:07:29.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, although that turned out to be a sham.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:39.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what you're saying is that Renge's\Naccomplice turned out to be her actual kidnapper?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:41.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that right, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:43.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.58,0:07:46.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:54.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, the problem is figuring out\Nwho that person could be, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:08:01.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there aren't many people a\Nyoung woman could easily turn to for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:07.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.57,0:08:09.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you happen to see something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.65,0:08:11.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:15.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, isn't that just a construction site?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:17.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, if I remember right, wasn't there...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.95,0:08:18.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there was!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.79,0:08:19.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:21.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.79,0:08:22.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:24.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,0:08:26.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.46,0:08:27.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In another part of town...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.51,0:08:41.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.27,0:08:43.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.64,0:08:46.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.02,0:08:47.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:53.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.11,0:08:54.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They got away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:55.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.41,0:08:56.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:01.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.45,0:09:03.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.84,0:09:15.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He turned right at that corner, Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:15.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:16.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.56,0:09:25.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oonuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.23,0:09:27.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:29.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:33.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:39.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They ordered me on the cell phone\Nto ditch the police and come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:44.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when I parked my car, all of the sudden-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.76,0:09:59.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:01.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Emergency, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.93,0:10:02.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well? What about the hostage?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:08.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He will return her after he has confirmed her safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:09.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He told us to wait until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.98,0:10:12.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it, making this some kind of joke...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:17.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Officer Takagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.07,0:10:22.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle Mouri told me to ask you to\Ncheck something really quick for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:24.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm really busy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:26.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:30.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The play was also progressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:36.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The first nobleman, Prince Ishizukuri, was told to bring\Nthe stone beggar bowl that the Buddha himself had used.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.51,0:10:41.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The second nobleman, Prince Kuramochi, was told to\Ntravel to bring back a branch from a tree on Mt. Horai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:46.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The third nobleman, Sadaijin Dainagon, was told to\Nfind a robe made from the pelts of flameproof rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.35,0:10:49.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:53.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come back quickly, Renge{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}... Tamanosuke{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.15,0:11:38.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course I was not looking behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.08,0:11:46.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys can't come in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.83,0:11:50.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not allowed to cross the yellow line!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.04,0:11:51.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.37,0:11:54.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, did you catch him in the emergency deployment?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.17,0:11:59.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? It hasn't even been a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:02.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! I just said you can't go in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.43,0:12:04.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were there any witnesses?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.64,0:12:07.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, aren't you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.43,0:12:09.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter. What about the witnesses?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:11.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When that guy was attacked!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.89,0:12:15.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So no one was watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.11,0:12:18.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It happened immediately after I got out of my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.38,0:12:40.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those are...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.22,0:12:44.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Security cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.89,0:12:51.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:53.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is it, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.10,0:12:53.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:57.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:12:59.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.23,0:13:01.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are there any clues in that video?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:05.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that camera doesn't show the actual scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.16,0:13:08.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. But the culprit-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:09.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:13.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop fooling around!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.87,0:13:15.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.46,0:13:16.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you were okay with it, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:19.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it was something like that, so-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:21.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.47,0:13:27.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Did it come?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.43,0:13:29.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:30.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.72,0:13:31.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:34.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gather everyone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:35.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.69,0:13:39.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I also have one more request...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:40.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.11,0:13:47.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:48.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.66,0:13:49.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:50.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.74,0:13:55.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I requested that the\Ninvestigation headquarters forward this to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.75,0:13:59.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The problem is the chimney in this picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:02.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was actually demolished four days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:04.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:08.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They got rid of it because the\Npublic bathhouse was being remodeled.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:13.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, this picture was\Nnot taken at the time it was sent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:15.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.43,0:14:21.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they had the e-mail prepared beforehand,\Nthe sender could have been with the recipient.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.77,0:14:26.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-So you're trying to say that the\Nculprit was someone she knew personally?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:27.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.99,0:14:28.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:31.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} asked me to look into some things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:34.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I found that this time, the culprit sent\Nthe e-mail they had prepared beforehand...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:36.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Always took the phone calls...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:40.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And is someone who could come into\Ndirect contact with her without being suspected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:47.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,L-Let's not joke around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.13,0:14:53.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please take a look at the video from the security camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:15:03.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oonuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you said you followed the\Nculprit's directions and tried to ditch the police, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.77,0:15:04.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is precisely correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:06.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.23,0:15:07.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"When?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:10.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the traffic light.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:14.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure the officers also heard the conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.03,0:15:17.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we didn't hear the culprit's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:20.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I was on the phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.87,0:15:24.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you really receive a call?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.09,0:15:27.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you implying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.05,0:15:33.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, why did the culprit take the\Ncell phone in addition to the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.01,0:15:35.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:40.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:41.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:43.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.06,0:15:45.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:48.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:51.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As you can see here, he isn't using his cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.99,0:15:55.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you checked his cell phone, there\Nwouldn't be a record of a call in the call log.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.91,0:15:57.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he didn't leave it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:16:03.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He most likely hid it somewhere, along with the ransom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.63,0:16:07.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we searched the whole area, we'd probably find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.67,0:16:11.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But before that, we must rescue the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.34,0:16:13.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:16.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only the culprit knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:21.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.39,0:16:23.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.02,0:16:24.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't lie, Oonuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.78,0:16:32.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is my daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:34.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is Renge?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:36.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chairman...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.62,0:16:39.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If something happens to my\Ndaughter, I won't let you get away with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.91,0:16:41.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.25,0:16:43.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-T-That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.25,0:16:46.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She asked me to help, so I-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.71,0:16:47.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Help?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:52.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. It started out as a fake kidnapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.05,0:16:56.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, Renge{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} would be\Nable to mention her accomplice's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:16:59.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And since her accomplice is also her real kidnapper...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:04.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He can't allow her to return safely by any means.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.89,0:17:07.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you intended to murder her from the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:08.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.98,0:17:10.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.53,0:17:12.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm definitely not going to tell you people anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.24,0:17:15.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not going anywhere, Oonuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:27.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to protect Kaguya, Mikado sent an\Nentire troop of 2,000 soldiers to prevent her departure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:29.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:32.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll definitely find Renge{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-oneesan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.76,0:17:34.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:42.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Boys! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.60,0:17:43.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:51.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Big brother, hurry and come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.23,0:17:52.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I'm right, it should be around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:54.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.82,0:17:56.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.40,0:17:57.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.24,0:17:58.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weeds?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:18:02.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why are they muddy when it hasn't even rained?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.12,0:18:04.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were they growing near water?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.08,0:18:05.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:16.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shan't let her go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.13,0:18:19.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tamanosuke{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:26.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shan't let you return to the moon, Kaguya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.19,0:18:31.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh, no way! Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:34.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or, if thou wilt not cease, be but sworn my love...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:37.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I shall depart from this country and my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.53,0:18:45.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tamanosuke{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s eyes aren't\Nlooking at Princess Kaguya nor at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:48.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Won't thou trust me and stay by my side?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:53.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaguya, always and forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:18:59.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the culprit was alone, and\Nwas thinking of all of this on the spot...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.38,0:19:02.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think he had enough time to have taken her too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.05,0:19:05.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means the next possible place is nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.02,0:19:06.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.31,0:19:08.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somewhere with water, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.44,0:19:08.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.14,0:19:09.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:16.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The light that shined in the dark night\Nseemed brighter than the sun in midday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.19,0:19:21.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A great cloud descended from the moon\Nbringing with it a great host of moon-folk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:40.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found her, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.19,0:19:52.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Renge{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-oneesan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.98,0:19:54.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about the play?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.23,0:19:56.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened to the play?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:19:59.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, Kaguya, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.11,0:20:01.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To the moon where thou belongs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:10.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this is it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.12,0:20:12.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I can't watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.84,0:20:19.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Renge{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.17,0:20:20.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Renge?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.59,0:20:22.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.05,0:20:25.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've caused so much trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.14,0:20:27.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't go out there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.06,0:20:31.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Renge{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:32.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.19,0:20:35.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For the sake of both Tamanosuke{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.95,0:20:39.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.99,0:20:44.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:47.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Renge{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.30,0:21:07.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We shalt meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.30,0:21:08.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe we shall.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.56,0:21:09.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaguya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.81,0:21:12.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, Renge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.48,0:21:14.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.77,0:21:16.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.82,0:21:28.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sort of disappointed, but it was a beautiful play.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:44.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop the world and hold me tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.17,0:21:48.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to be closer to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.05,0:21:54.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've fallen for you time and time again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.43,0:22:00.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My tears overflow as the dawn approaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.86,0:22:08.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The warmth you give me makes me forget to take a breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.83,0:22:18.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I'm afraid of losing the feeling of your fingertips stroking my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.00,0:22:29.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The attraction that pulls us together...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.14,0:22:39.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should we be separated tomorrow, I would search for you to no end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.31,0:22:45.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop the world and smile gently...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.57,0:22:49.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I will always be by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.24,0:22:55.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let the light of dawn shine upon you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.75,0:23:02.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And envelop the two us of like this forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.01,0:23:07.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, Oonuki was arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.88,0:23:09.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ransom was also found.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.55,0:23:15.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like Princess Kaguya, Renge{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} returned home...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.85,0:23:19.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And finally convinced her father\Nto let her stay in the theater troupe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.98,0:23:23.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She is now traveling the world with\NTamanosuke{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and the rest of the troupe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.82,0:23:36.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was also the beginning of\NTamanosuke{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s and Renge{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s new life together.
